    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387100/extras/d7467096c5ab969fc40395a7de7e67d9.poster.avif?t=1727954306\" width=32 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387100/extras/d7467096c5ab969fc40395a7de7e67d9.webm?t=1727954306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Get ready for a dino-mite adventure! Derpy Dino is a 2D survival game where you play as a lovable, yet hapless dinosaur trying to survive in a world filled with danger. In Survival Mode, dodge falling meteors and see how long you can last. The timer will keep track of your progress. But that's not all! In the brand new Adventure Mode you can take on five levels filled with dangerous enemies and delicious fruits!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387100/extras/89ec574426321b40963712cc687a998e.poster.avif?t=1727954306\" width=32 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387100/extras/89ec574426321b40963712cc687a998e.webm?t=1727954306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387100/extras/e0c4f6dcfa7fb002355c816bd5d867e0.apng?t=1727954306\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387100/extras/e0c4f6dcfa7fb002355c816bd5d867e0.poster.avif?t=1727954306\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=64 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387100/extras/59ef467d193f03116495962381bea483.webp?t=1727954306\"><img src=\"